title: Breaking Bad Season 4
description:
The story of Breaking Bad is set in Albuquerque, New Mexico (which is also produced), and revolves around Walter White (Bryan Cranston), a chemistry teacher in high school / middle unappreciated with a teenage son who suffers from cerebral palsy (RJ Mitte) and pregnant wife, Skyler (Anna Gunn). When the already tense White is diagnosed with lung cancer, he collapses and embraces a life of crime, producing and selling methamphetamine with his former student Jesse Pinkman (Aaron Paul) with the aim of ensuring the financial future of your family in the event of his death.
